==English==

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|[plʌs]}}

===Etymology===
From {{L.}} ''[[plus#Latin|plus]]'' "more".

===Conjunction===
'''plus'''

#in addition to which
#{{arithmetic}} [[increase]]d by
#:''One '''plus''' one is two.''

